@startuml
title UML State Machine Diagram

[*] --> Initial

state Initial
Initial --> CreateUser : [create account]

state CreateUser
CreateUser --> AccountCreated : [account created]

state AccountCreated
AccountCreated --> BrowseVideos : [browse videos]
AccountCreated --> UploadVideo : [upload videos]

state BrowseVideos
BrowseVideos --> UploadVideo : [upload video]
BrowseVideos --> LikedVideos : [like video]
BrowseVideos --> SavedVideos : [view saved videos]
BrowseVideos --> Discussion : [enter discussion]

state UploadVideo
UploadVideo --> BrowseVideos : [video uploaded]

state LikedVideos
LikedVideos --> SavedVideos : [view saved]

state SavedVideos
SavedVideos --> BrowseVideos : [back to browse]
SavedVideos --> Discussion : [enter discussion]

state Discussion
Discussion --> [*] : [discussion completed]

@enduml
